data.description: Step into this Charming Mid-Century Modern home, built in 1952 and Embraced by Tranquil, Tree-Shaded surroundings. The single-level layout features a Living Room, bathed in Natural Light and serves as a Welcoming Gathering space, while a Separate Family Room offers Intimacy and Warmth for Cherished Moments with Loved Ones, the Remodeled Kitchen boasts Custom Cabinets and Breakfast Bar combining Style and Functionality, along with 3 Bedrooms and 3 Baths catering to your Family's Needs and Providing Ample Space. Embrace the Allure of the Sun Porch, a haven for Relaxation and year-round Enjoyment, the thoughtful Design of this Lovely Home also includes a Laundry room for convenience and practicality. Step outside to discover the Sparkling Pool, a Refreshing Retreat for hot summer days and perfect for Entertaining. The Property features a 1-car garage transformed into a versatile Workshop, along with 2 Covered Carport areas for Multiple Vehicles! Conveniently Located to Schools & Library!
